cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with image denoising using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The authors also mention fine-tuning the network for specific semantic classes, which involves machine learning techniques such as transfer learning and fine-tuning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of existing image classifiers, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper proposes a new neural network architecture, which is a common topic in neural networks (cs.NE).
